/*****************************************************************************
 *   adctest.c:  main C entry file for NXP LPC11xx Family Microprocessors
 *
 *   Copyright(C) 2008, NXP Semiconductor
 *   All rights reserved.
 *
 *   History
 *   2009.12.07  ver 1.00    Preliminary version, first Release
